===Etymology 1===
{{zh-forms|s=谂|alt=恁,惗}}
Probably a {{der|yue|qfa-tak}} substrate word. Compare {{cog|za|naemj||to think}} and {{cog|tyz|nẳm||to think}}. This root occurs in several {{cog|za|-}} dialects and {{cog|hmx-mie|-}}, and in Liuzhou Mandarin ''nɐn⁵⁴''.

{{zh-ref|Bai (1980)}} associates this word with {{zh-l|*恁|to think}}.

{{zh-ref|Bauer (1996)}} argues the direction of borrowing of this word is not certain, and it is just as likely that {{cog|za|-}} and/or {{cog|hmx-mie|-}} borrowed it from Cantonese as the other way round. This root does not seem to occur in the {{cog|tbq|-}} languages.

